Presley, who gave his last performance in early summer 1977, had been expected to start his next tour the following day.Presley's daughter, Lisa Marie Presley, who was married to Michael Jackson from 1994-1996, wrote on her Myspace blog on Friday that Jackson feared he would meet the same fate as Lisa Marie's father.
